333
00:38:20,600 --> 00:38:26,100
Is that child really a sacred bone?

334
00:38:26,160 --> 00:38:31,270
Do you think it's coincidence that your son and mine grew up together?

335
00:38:31,270 --> 00:38:36,920
Just as you saved that child, I too did it to save your child.

336
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:41,290
Ji Soo also, with the world not knowing anything,

337
00:38:42,050 --> 00:38:45,340
I wished for him to hide like that.

338
00:39:00,670 --> 00:39:02,330
Wonhwa Joon Jeong.

339
00:39:03,070 --> 00:39:05,440
What is going on?

340
00:39:05,440 --> 00:39:09,360
I am dying right now.

341
00:39:11,270 --> 00:39:13,220
The child...

342
00:39:14,030 --> 00:39:17,930
Please save the child.

343
00:39:20,440 --> 00:39:22,560
Joon Jeong.

344
00:39:53,500 --> 00:39:55,610
Fate?

345
00:39:59,360 --> 00:40:03,290
I won't let someone hurt you like this again.

346
00:40:06,170 --> 00:40:08,620
I'll make sure that person will never

347
00:40:10,760 --> 00:40:13,480
be able to harm you again.

348
00:40:14,400 --> 00:40:16,230
I promise.

349
00:40:38,980 --> 00:40:41,940
You did something unnecessarily.

350
00:40:48,300 --> 00:40:49,690
Let go.

351
00:40:49,690 --> 00:40:55,400
I know. That you can go alone. However, right now,

352
00:40:55,400 --> 00:40:58,130
I'm here not as a Hwarang but as Your Highness' bodyguard.

353
00:40:59,280 --> 00:41:03,200
So, please allow me to do so.

354
00:41:07,190 --> 00:41:10,500
A child like you is going to protect me?

355
00:41:11,300 --> 00:41:15,080
I'm not a child, but young.

356
00:41:15,080 --> 00:41:20,160
Enough for my heart to race wildly whenever I look at you.

357
00:41:22,360 --> 00:41:26,890
Until the chief guard recovers, I will protect you.

358
00:41:35,500 --> 00:41:40,620
The king that I wish for is one who can protect his people and

359
00:41:40,620 --> 00:41:43,760
the people who need protection.

360
00:41:43,760 --> 00:41:47,940
A king who can protect the weak, the kind, the wounded, the abandoned,

361
00:41:47,940 --> 00:41:51,500
those kinds of people.

362
00:41:51,500 --> 00:41:57,500
So tell me. If I have the justification or whatever to my name,

363
00:41:57,500 --> 00:42:00,850
and I can protect those people,

364
00:42:01,460 --> 00:42:05,810
I am thinking of giving it a try. Being the king.

365
00:42:07,360 --> 00:42:11,540
Even though there's a king, you want to become the King?

366
00:42:51,200 --> 00:42:55,850
Ah Ro, it's Father.

367
00:42:57,600 --> 00:42:59,370
Are you alright?

368
00:43:02,300 --> 00:43:04,560
What about Orabeoni?

369
00:43:08,100 --> 00:43:13,090
He's alright. He's okay.

370
00:43:16,900 --> 00:43:20,560
I'm sorry, Father.

371
00:43:27,430 --> 00:43:32,170
It's alright. Now everything's fine.

372
00:43:33,410 --> 00:43:35,680
Where is he?

373
00:43:38,400 --> 00:43:43,260
Where is Orabeoni?

374
00:43:47,550 --> 00:43:50,180
Have you prepared your heart?

375
00:43:52,950 --> 00:43:56,360
It seems you haven't yet.

376
00:43:59,000 --> 00:44:02,330
This isn't your choice.

377
00:44:02,330 --> 00:44:05,630
Through you, it's Silla's choice.

378
00:44:05,630 --> 00:44:10,700
Think about the Cheonin village you lived in with Mak Moon.

379
00:44:10,700 --> 00:44:16,170
The choice you're about to make will be the most important and meaningful one.

380
00:44:18,500 --> 00:44:21,400
There's someone who wants to meet you.

381
00:44:44,600 --> 00:44:49,090
I heard you quit being Poong Wol Joo so why did you ask me to come here?

382
00:44:57,410 --> 00:44:59,280
Were you surprised?

383
00:45:00,360 --> 00:45:03,580
I know you don't have good feelings towards me.

384
00:45:05,800 --> 00:45:08,330
No, you wouldn't know,

385
00:45:08,330 --> 00:45:12,140
because it's much worse than what you think.

386
00:45:13,550 --> 00:45:16,830
This is why I confuse you as Sam Maek Jong, don't you think?

387
00:45:16,830 --> 00:45:21,340
What's the reason you came here? For what reason did you want to meet me?

388
00:45:23,850 --> 00:45:26,750
I'm thinking of making you king.

389
00:45:28,900 --> 00:45:35,900
What a pity. Haven't you heard from Hwi Gyeong Gong about me?

390
00:45:37,190 --> 00:45:41,220
Do you really think that I would accept help from someone like you?

391
00:45:41,220 --> 00:45:43,600
Yes, I do.

392
00:45:44,510 --> 00:45:45,560
How so?

393
00:45:45,560 --> 00:45:49,100
Because that's what power is about.

394
00:45:49,100 --> 00:45:52,170
Unless you wield it, you will succumb to it.

395
00:45:54,620 --> 00:45:58,560
Until now, haven't you always been the victim?

396
00:45:58,560 --> 00:46:01,330
That's why you want to become king.

397
00:46:01,330 --> 00:46:06,000
So, don't you think you should make a decision?

398
00:46:06,000 --> 00:46:08,700
Whether to wield it or succumb to it.

399
00:46:11,000 --> 00:46:14,670
No. The choice is mine to make,

400
00:46:14,670 --> 00:46:18,860
because the one who seems desperate because you need me

401
00:46:18,860 --> 00:46:21,230
appears to be you.

402
00:46:22,520 --> 00:46:27,760
This must be power. If I don't wield it, succumbing to it.

403
00:46:39,100 --> 00:46:44,910
Why don't you stay by my side? Where did you go?

404
00:46:47,020 --> 00:46:50,030
So you're still alive.

405
00:47:07,400 --> 00:47:10,170
What brings you here?

406
00:47:16,620 --> 00:47:18,720
Am I scary?

407
00:47:20,730 --> 00:47:22,410
If you...

408
00:47:26,900 --> 00:47:30,120
If you trade places with me, you should know.

409
00:47:30,120 --> 00:47:32,400
This isn't the first or second time.

410
00:47:32,400 --> 00:47:34,830
I saved your brother.

411
00:47:34,830 --> 00:47:39,960
You only put your brother in danger. I'm the one who saves him.

412
00:47:39,960 --> 00:47:43,050
It seems you hoped that I would die.

413
00:47:43,630 --> 00:47:47,970
Yes. I did.

414
00:47:47,970 --> 00:47:53,630
More than you think, your brother is a precious person. I could protect him if it weren't for you!

415
00:47:57,050 --> 00:48:01,760
Although I already told you, I will survive

416
00:48:01,760 --> 00:48:04,440
no matter what,

417
00:48:04,440 --> 00:48:08,400
because I know better than anyone else

418
00:48:08,400 --> 00:48:11,350
that is what my brother wishes.

419
00:48:11,350 --> 00:48:13,960
So,

420
00:48:13,960 --> 00:48:18,500
no matter what you say, no matter how you try to shake me up,

421
00:48:19,380 --> 00:48:21,640
it's no use.

422
00:48:22,430 --> 00:48:25,370
I'll protect my brother.

423
00:48:26,510 --> 00:48:31,300
I'll protect my man.

424
00:48:32,200 --> 00:48:36,200
You say everything with your mouth.

425
00:48:36,200 --> 00:48:40,120
But, I can really protect Seon Woo.

426
00:48:40,120 --> 00:48:44,160
Wherever, whatever the situation, from whomever!

427
00:48:57,200 --> 00:49:00,310
We'll have to change the king.

428
00:49:04,100 --> 00:49:07,930
Then, after taking Jin Heung down from the throne,

429
00:49:07,930 --> 00:49:11,270
