430
00:49:24,600 --> 00:49:28,530
Your Highness, His Majesty has arrived.

431
00:49:54,700 --> 00:49:56,430
Your complexion is pale.

432
00:49:56,430 --> 00:50:00,400
Did you sit on the throne to be treated in that fashion by Gagkan?

433
00:50:01,230 --> 00:50:03,900
You gave them an excuse.

434
00:50:03,900 --> 00:50:09,530
It is something which will shake the foundation of the Silla's Sacred Bone System and cause contempt for the royal family.

435
00:50:09,530 --> 00:50:13,320
It's because of you. It's all because of you.

436
00:50:13,320 --> 00:50:15,220
I will prevail.

437
00:50:15,220 --> 00:50:19,140
