444
00:50:41,930 --> 00:50:45,860
Through my Hwarang, I will dominate them.

445
00:50:45,860 --> 00:50:48,100
Hwarang?

446
00:50:48,740 --> 00:50:53,540
You haven't the slightest clue what the Hwarang are to you.

447
00:50:54,330 --> 00:50:56,530
Seon Woo.

448
00:50:57,340 --> 00:51:00,030
Seon Woo is Hwi Gyeong Gong's son.

449
00:51:02,110 --> 00:51:04,580
That child also has the blood of the sacred bone.

450
00:51:04,580 --> 00:51:08,390
He's another sacred bone who will cause war over the throne!

451
00:51:08,390 --> 00:51:12,910
He's your rival who will strangle you!

452
00:51:26,830 --> 00:51:28,960
I mean, you still didn't know?

453
00:51:28,960 --> 00:51:32,950
Of course, she woke up. A while ago!

454
00:51:43,210 --> 00:51:46,820
I should've just said something to him.

455
00:51:48,010 --> 00:51:51,730
But, I have nothing to say.

456
00:51:56,120 --> 00:51:59,390
Am I really a burden?

457
00:52:01,490 --> 00:52:04,480
No, I'm not!

458
00:52:06,690 --> 00:52:09,240
I almost totally stopped myself.

459
00:52:10,580 --> 00:52:15,140
Why isn't Orabeoni coming? I'm awake.

460
00:52:19,520 --> 00:52:22,800
Yoo Beom Gong Gwa?

461
00:52:24,060 --> 00:52:28,440
Even if there's someone who comes at you, endure it?

462
00:52:50,210 --> 00:52:54,000
You... Are you all right?

